## My Understanding of DevOps & Cloud

**DevOps** is not a tool — it is a culture of shared ownership between development and operations. It means faster, safer delivery through automation, monitoring, and continuous improvement.

**Cloud Engineering** is the skill of building and managing scalable, reliable infrastructure on platforms like AWS/Azure/GCP — treating infrastructure as code, not as manual setup.

As an SDET, I tested what developers built. As a DevOps engineer, I will own the entire pipeline — from code commit to production.

---

