## Consistency Strategy

- Push at least one commit every day to the `90DaysOfDevOps` repo
- Write a 3-line daily log: *what I learned, what confused me, what I'll do tomorrow*
- Review weekly output every Sunday before planning the next week
- No skipping — if time is short, 30 minutes beats zero

